ficantly enhance the conventional charge thermopower. Owing to\nthe Hanle effect, the thermopower can also be manipulated with a magnetic\nfield, producing a Hanle magnetothermopower.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2011 06:03:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-20"}
